content: wtfsayo: Merged an exceptional 59 pull requests in `elizaos/eliza`, focusing on a mix of bug fixes, new features, and significant enhancements to CI/CD and code quality workflows. A major cleanup effort was undertaken, most notably removing over 55,000 lines to fix the docs build configuration in `elizaos/eliza#5513`. Throughout this highly active week, they also provided 3 code reviews, 36 PR comments, and created 5 issues for code quality reports.
